{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Asgards_Fall_discord_banner.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Jormungandr_slim.gif?t=1738837099\" /><strong>Embark on an epic saga in Asgard's Fall, a norse Survivors-like Roguelite. Fight your way through hordes of creatures and let the gods feel your relentless wrath. How will your saga unfold?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/EN_headline_AHeroicSaga.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Warrior_Combat.gif?t=1738837099\" /><strong>You can choose from a variety of heroes to demonstrate your might in the battle against Asgard, such as the fierce Warrior and the agile Huntress, each with their own distinct skill tree. Do you have the courage to face the hordes and leaders of the Nine Realms?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/EN_headline_AbilitySystem.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/ChooseAbility.gif?t=1738837099\" /><strong>Master the art of combat with the dynamic Ability System. Choose from a diverse array of skills, each tailored to your playstyle. Unleash devastating attacks, strategic buffs, and unique powers to conquer the Nine Realms. Forge your hero's destiny!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/EN_headline_WebOfWyrd.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Web_of_Wyrd.gif?t=1738837099\" /><strong>Behold the Web of Wyrd, where the threads of destiny are woven by your own hand. Forge your fate by placing powerful knots into the Web of Wyrd, further enhancing your strength on your path to conquering Asgard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/EN_headline_Warpaints.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Warpaint.gif?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A meta-progression system where you unlock Warpaint runes that modify and amplify your characters' abilities. It features an inventory management system, challenging you to fit as many effective runes as possible into a limited space, maximizing their impact on your abilities, playstyle, and strategy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Warpaint runes can be found during battle or crafted using pigments looted from enemies or discovered in Yggdrasil's Gift caches.</strong>\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/EN_headline_SkillTrees.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Stone_of_Seidr.gif?t=1738837099\" /><strong>Shape your hero's evolution with our intricate Skill Tree. Customize your playstyle by unlocking diverse abilities, enhancing strengths, and adapting to challenges. Every choice influences your saga's outcome. Craft a hero uniquely suited to your journey through the Nine Realms!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/AF_Steam_strich.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Huntress_Combat.gif?t=1738837099\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738837099","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738837099","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/55726c3c210e1b2755d89e6a1672080ad3e5f4bf/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738837099","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/55726c3c210e1b2755d89e6a1672080ad3e5f4bf/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738837099","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Asgards_Fall_discord_banner.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/Jormungandr_slim.gif?t=1738837099\" /><strong>Embark on an epic saga in Asgard's Fall, a norse Survivors-like Roguelite. Fight your way through hordes of creatures and let the gods feel your relentless wrath. How will your saga unfold?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780710/extras/EN_headline_AHeroicSaga.png?t=1738837099\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_i